data.description: Cozy, well maintained 3 bedroom, 1 bath, 1 car garage home centrally located close to shopping, schools, golf course & more.  Home has a pellet stove in addition to electric baseboard heating to keep the home comfortable & warm.  In recent years new exterior stucco siding, new interior paint, new vinyl plank flooring throughout, new baseboard & interior trim, new front door, new electrical & plumbing fixtures, new water heater, new washer/dryer & microwave have been updated. Lrg backyard w/patio to enjoy.
